name: Arche ch.1 ep3
description:
Hi! Thank you for reading ch1.3
A possession has happened hahaha I’m honestly not sure what to write for this, except that I was starting to figure out my style better!

Thank you for reading so far (and a bigger thank you if you purchased a chapter! It really helps me out with my goal of becoming a full time webcomic artist). Again, if you want to see some BTS (not the boy group), follow me on twitter @feireina
Lots of Love,
Fei
